atha śikṣārakṣaṇādhikāre kim iti cittaṃ rakṣyata ity āha—na śikṣeti. anyathā śikṣaiva rakṣitum aśakyā calam anāyattaṃ cittam arakṣatā, cittasya calatāyāṃ śikṣāyāḥ sthairyāyogāt.

<commentary>ito 'pi cittam eva rakṣaṇīyam ity āha.

aparikarmitā mattavaravāraṇā na janayanti tāṃ pīḍām iha loke. paraloke avīcyādau yāṃ karoti svacchandatayāvasthitaṃ cittam eva mataṅgaja eva, tathāgatājñāṅkuśena kathaṃcid vaśīkriyamāṇatvāt.
</commentary>

tasyāyattīkaraṇe guṇam āha. yadi baddhaḥ kathaṃcid bhavet. smṛtir vakṣyamāṇalakṣaṇā. saiva rajjur bandhanopāyatvāt.